fields.name: White Sunglasses
fields.description: Funky sunglasses in a flattering and classic white colour to bring out all the classy dogs out there. Your pooch can rock them on those sunny days or when you all go on holiday!

fields.name: Red Beret
fields.description: Let your dog express their colourful side with this knitted red beret.

fields.name: Yellow Beanie
fields.description: It will feel like the sun has come out when your furry one wears this lovely knitted yellow beanie. It even has a pom pom on top!

fields.name: Pink Party Hat
fields.description: When your girl doggie wants to be a princess...the pink party hat with decorative band will do just that. Bright and special.

fields.name: Christmas Hat
fields.description: Merry Christmas! When your dog wants to join in with the festive spirit. This is a traditional red and white Christmas hat for your dog. One size fits all.

fields.name: Elf Hat
fields.description: Make your dog feel festive with this cute elf hat! Green background with red plait, with a pair of ears to finish it off.

fields.name: Reindeer Antlers
fields.description: Carrying on with the Christmas theme, this is a pair of reindeer antlers in brown. Just pop it over your dog's head like a hairband and they will be transformed.

fields.name: Star Bandana
fields.description: All cool dogs like a bandana! Get your dog to stand out with this cotton bandana in blue background with white stars.

fields.name: Pawprint and Bones Bandana
fields.description: For special occasions, nothing looks better than this light blue bandana with cute colourful pawprints and bones in bright colours.

fields.name: Yellow Bandana
fields.description: This bandana can be used on the neck or, just like our model does, as a hairband. Flattering yellow cotton with a flower design in red and white.

fields.name: Yellow Hoodie
fields.description: Funky yellow hoodie for the cool doggos out there

fields.name: Colourful Rubber Knot
fields.description: Does your puppy need to chew but can't find anything suitable? This rubber knot will do the trick. Endless chewing hours with no damage, and they can even play fetch with it since it rolls.

fields.name: Frilly skirt
fields.description: Is your dog a princess? She sure will feel like one with this cute skirt. It's frilly and has a nice classic check pattern.

fields.name: Denim Dungarees
fields.description: Your dog will rock these dungarees in classic blue denim.

fields.name: Green & Red Onesie
fields.description: Keep your dog warm with this cosy onesie, all in red with green accents on the sleeves. Just the festive touch that your dog needs!

fields.name: Denim jeans
fields.description: Get those doggie friends' tails wagging with pure jealousy when they see your dog rocking these amazing jeans! In denim with a contemporary cut and classic blue wash, these will become your go-to piece for sure.

fields.name: Red Dress
fields.description: Mirror mirror on the wall, who's the prettiest of them all? The answer will be 'Your dog' once she wears this stunning red and white dress this summer! With frills and a little accent in pink, you will love dressing her in this.

fields.name: Soft Toy Trio
fields.description: Treat your best friend to this magnificent trio of soft, plush toys for hours of fun! You will receive one broccoli toy, one carrot toy and last but not least, one donut toy.  Hours of entertainment and fun for your little one!
